# SEO Rankings Analyzer Requirements Documentation

## Core Dependencies
- `streamlit>=1.31.0`
  - Core web application framework
  - Powers the interactive dashboard interface
  - Handles UI components and state management

- `pandas>=2.2.0`
  - Data manipulation and analysis library
  - Used for processing ranking data
  - Creates dataframes for analysis and report generation

- `requests>=2.31.0`
  - HTTP library for external API communication
  - Makes calls to ValueSERP API
  - Handles response processing

## Location Processing
- `geopy>=2.4.1`
  - Geocoding and location validation
  - Verifies user-input locations
  - Ensures location data accuracy

## Time and Date Handling
- `pytz>=2024.1`
  - Timezone handling library
  - Used for report generation timestamps
  - Ensures consistent time formatting

## Report Generation
- `Jinja2>=3.1.3`
  - HTML template engine
  - Generates professional HTML reports
  - Handles dynamic content insertion

- `XlsxWriter>=3.1.9`
  - Excel file creation
  - Generates downloadable Excel reports
  - Handles formatting and data export

## API Management
- `ratelimit>=2.2.1`
  - Rate limiting decorator
  - Controls API request frequency
  - Prevents API quota exhaustion
